For the condition expressed in Eq. 3.239 to hold for every T ≥ 0, we must have

q(t) = q˜δ(t), .............................................................. (3.240)

where  δ(t)  is  the  Dirac  delta  function  satisfying  the  properties  expressed  by  Eqs.  3.185  and
3.186.

